Directory Lister
------------------------------------------------------------------
Directory Lister is a simple PHP based script created to let you list the
contents of a directory and all sub directories and allow you to navigate
there within.  Just download and install Directory Lister to any web
directory and have immediate access to all files and sub-direcories under
that directory.

More info available at http://www.directorylister.com


Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------
To install Directory Lister, simply upload index.php and the 
.directory-lister folder to the directory that you would like to have 
listed and view the page in your browser.

More detailed instructions at http://www.directorylister.com/installation


